	     <tr><td id="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top"><a id="sj" href="/db/item.html?item=13515&amp;mid=105085358779982">Easy way to have this made</a> <a id="fs8" href="/db/item.html?item=13515&amp;mid=105085358779982#post"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." width="17" height="11" /></a>
	     <br clear="all" /><small>Posted @ Sun, Apr 20th 12:24 PM 2003</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=203293"><span id=" ">Ellivoc</span></a><br /><span id="notbold">14 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score:</span> Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>Ok I've looked at the recipe for this and there is any easier way to get this made.<br/><br/>-Akheva Blood can be bought in the Bazaar.<br/>-Essence of Darkness can be bought in the Bazaar.<br/>-Sapphires can be bought from venders.&nbsp;&nbsp;I got mine from the one in PoK with my charisma at 135 for only 104pp ea.<br/>-Poison Vials can be bought from venders.  There are several in different zones, but I got mine in PoK.<br/><br/>-For the combinations it's easy to find an Enchanter to make the Vial of Distilled Mana.<br/>-Find a Brewer with a skill better than the 138 Trivial for the Black Acrylia Temper.<br/>-For the Sheet of Black Acrylia find a Smith with a skill better than the 117 Trivial required<br/>-For the final combination you can probably find a Smith with a skill of 250.  I found one that will do the combination for me.  It will cost me 500pp if he is successful.<br/><br/>For all I've spent(will spend), it's not a bad price to pay for a weapon I can sell for thousands of plat when I get my epic.  Or give to one of my lower characters.<br/><br/>The easiest way to get these combinations done is if someone in your guild has the skills.<br/><br/>Good Luck.  This is a very nice weapon till the Druid Epic Scimitar.<br/><br/><em id=fs8>Edited, Sun Apr 20 11:49:40 2003</em></p>&nbsp;<br /></td></tr>
